tests: assert parse_music('o| o| o| o| o| o| o| o| o| o') == [2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2]
assert parse_music('o o| o| o| o| o| o| o| o| o o o o') == [4, 2, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4]
assert parse_music('o o| o| o| o| o| o| o| o| o o') == [4, 2, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4, 4]
assert sort_numbers('nine eight seven six five four three two one zero') == 'zero one two three four five six seven eight nine'
assert sort_numbers('zero four eight') == 'zero four eight'
assert sort_numbers('seven nine three') == 'three seven nine'
assert sort_numbers('five two one') == 'one two five'
assert is_bored("The sky is blue. The sun is shining. I love this weather") == 1
assert is_bored("I am bored. Are you bored? Yes, I am bored!") == 3
assert is_bored("I am not bored. I am happy!") == 2
assert encode('This is a message') == 'tHKS KS C MGSSCGG'
assert words_string("Hi, my name is John") == ["Hi", "my", "name", "is", "John"]
assert words_string("One, two, three, four, five, six") == ["One", "two", "three", "four", "five", "six"]
assert histogram('a b c a b') == {'a': 2, 'b': 2}
assert odd_count(['1234567']) == ["the number of odd elements 4n the str4ng 4 of the 4nput."]
assert odd_count(['3',"11111111"]) == ["the number of odd elements 1n the str1ng 1 of the 1nput.", "the number of odd elements 8n the str8ng 8 of the 8nput."]
assert select_words("Mary had a little lamb", 4) == ["little"]
assert select_words("Mary had a little lamb", 3) == ["Mary", "lamb"]
assert words_in_sentence("a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z") == "a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x z"
assert words_in_sentence("lets go for swimming") == "go for"
